{"tid":2242383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［要睇就快］歷史博物館「香港故事」常設展翻新 據報移除歷任港督照 將提佔領運動等 97 後事件","createTime":"2020-10-14T03:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T04:10:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3280404dc0eb62216e2ab597320ea6b983088a19","tid":2242383,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"開幕 19 年的香港歷史博物館「香港故事」常設展，將於下周一（19 日）閉館，進行兩年翻新工程。港台引述消息指，翻新後展覽料將加入 97 後發生的事件，包括 2003 年沙士、2014 年雨傘運動等，但不會提反送中，並減少對敏感事件的文字描述，避免爭議。此外，港台亦引消息稱，展覽或移除現時在閣樓展出的歷任港督照片，但預計會展出港督的珍貴品。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》另向康樂及文化事務署查詢事件，有待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A8%AD%E5%B1%95%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E6%AD%B7%E4%BB%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%9D%A3%E7%85%A7-%E5%B0%87%E6%8F%90%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E7%AD%89-97-%E5%BE%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259D%25A3%25E7%2585%25A7-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25AD%2589-97-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%2F&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=0d214c1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%25AD